<PatchData Name="Shadow SX - 1.1">
	<Description>Expects CleanRip of the original Shadow the Hedgehog NTSC ROM.
Learn more at: https://wiibrew.org/wiki/CleanRip

Extra controls
Hold Z when entering stage in Select Mode to enable Practice Mode.
Hold D-Pad Up for Expert Mode for that stage.
Both can be held to enable Expert Mode Practice Mode.

Practice Mode Commands (Z + Button)
L = Fill Dark Meter
R = Fill Hero Meter
L + R = Clear Both Meters
D-Pad Up = Toggle Meter Value as Score
D-Pad Down = Toggle Timer State (Running, Paused, Reset)

Turbo Action Commmands (Built in ~10hz input)
L + B = Turbo B input
Z + A = Turbo A input</Description>
